Mash avocados with lime juice and ranch mix in large bowl until creamy and chunky. Add corn, onion, tomatoes, peppers and cilantro. Stir in cottage cheese. Spread mixture evenly onto 9x13 rectangular baking sheet. Place yogurt into pastry bag with small round tip. Use white yogurt to create yard lines and yard markers. Tuck tortilla chips (patsies) around the edges. Serve with remaining chips.